{
  "stem": "26983.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rivka. ?] She survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because she had to work and stay in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because she worked in a special job, which was important for German military equipment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Slate, you know, in that time they didn't have plastic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used slate for airplanes and heaven knows what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they worked for this slate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And therefore she survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If that time, I thought, well both of them--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a couple of-- I don't know how many, but there were-- anyhow this is one of the stories of the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were very strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a special look in their eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very special people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They got food as much as they wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got alcohol as much as they wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had in the time of evacuation of Jews from France, they could at my time do their cooking in the court yet, which was between our block and their block.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They cooked on liquor, on spirit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the spirit was perfume from the transports.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had so much of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to us children, they brought sometimes even a bit of chocolate or some cigarette.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could handle and change a cigarette for something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I can tell you another story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, this Kalman told me, this was not his only job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He also had to help in other jobs, what they have done when a woman transport came, and there was a very beautiful woman, they left her to the very end.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took off their clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean as if they gave here a kind of better treatment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes he brought to the camp this underwear from the nicest Frenchmen to our camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
